  "title": "Quantity Surveyor",
  "description": "<p>Responsibilities:</p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Prepare tender BQ costing &amp; submission, progress payment claims, VO &amp; finalization of accounts</li>\n  <li>Attend tender interviews/meetings</li>\n  <li>Liaise with main contractors, sub-contractors &amp;  project team</li>\n  <li>Liaise with suppliers for materials</li>\n  <li>Evaluation and certification of sub-contractors' progress payments</li>\n  <li>Able to read drawings</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Requirements:</p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Degree or Diploma in Quantity Surveying and/or Building and/or equivalent;</li>\n  <li>Preferably with min. 5 years experience in managing Architectural Works (Aluminium, Stainless Steel, Steel and Wet Trades) tender/quotation;</li>\n  <li>Goods costing knowledge and committed;</li>\n  <li>Proficient in Microsoft Office;</li>\n  <li>Confident &amp; able to work under pressure;</li>\n  <li>5.5 days work week</li>\n</ul>",
